{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 69,
  "title": "第六十九章（用兵）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "用兵有言曰 吾不敢為主而為客 不敢進寸而芮尺"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂行无行 攘无臂 執无兵 乃无敵矣"
    },
    {
      "text": "禍莫大於无適 无適近亡吾寶矣"
    },
    {
      "text": "故稱兵相若 則哀者勝矣"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "主，先也。不敢先舉兵。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "客者，和而不倡。用兵當承天而後動。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "侵人境界，利人財寶，為進；閉門守城，為退。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "彼遂不止，為天下賊，雖行誅之，不行執也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖欲大怒，若無臂可攘也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖欲仍引之，若無敵可仍也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖欲執持之，若無兵刃可持用也。何者？傷彼之民罹罪於天，遭不道之君，愍忍喪之痛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫禍亂之害，莫大於欺輕敵家，侵取不休，輕戰貪財也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "幾，近也。寶，身也。欺輕敵者，近喪身也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "兩敵戰也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "哀者慈仁，士卒不遠於死。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "彼遂不止。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "行，謂行陳也，言以謙退哀慈，不敢為物先，用戰猶行無行，攘無臂，執無兵，扔無敵也，言無有與之抗也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言吾哀慈謙退，非欲以取强，無敵於天下也。不得已而卒至於無敵，斯乃吾之所以為大禍也。寶，三寶也，故曰，幾亡吾寶。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "抗，舉也；加，當也。哀者，必相惜而不趣利避害，故必勝。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
